      "rationale": "Young's modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.1 GPa) sourced from certified coupon testing of the same Ti-6Al-4V ELI material lot used in physical constructs. Geometry derived from CAD files with dimensional verification against CMM measurements (max deviation 0.03 mm)."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
