      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and relative error < 10%. E/uval values: stiffness 0.87, yield force 1.42, force at 40 mm 1.61. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Eq. 3.2 incorporating both experimental uncertainty and model prediction uncertainty."
