      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the primary mechanical performance metrics specified in ASTM F1717 and directly relate to the device's ability to stabilize the spinal segment without fracture. These QoIs are clinically meaningful and align with FDA's expectations for spinal implant submissions."
    },
